name: TheBurpeeChallenge
0:
”Alexa, start The Burpee Challenge.”
”Alexa, tell The Burpee Challenge to log 10 burpees.”
”Alexa, ask The Burpee Challenge what are the high scores?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: the burpee challenge
des:
Burpees are an intense full-body workout. Often regarded as one of the most effective exercises (and one of the most difficult), completing this challenge will get you in the best shape of your life! To win the challenge and get your name put on the leader boards, do 10,000 burpees within 100 days!

"Brace yourselves, burpees are coming!"

~Help~ (say these commands within the skill for additional features)
-To log burpees manually "Log Burpees" or you could say "Log X burpees" where X is any number.
-For high scores "What are the high scores?"
-To reset the challenge "Reset Challenge."

Disclaimer: This is an intense workout. Please speak to a medical doctor before performing this challenge.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
